#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.81"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.81:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.81:0.2"
msgid "9. Theravagga "
msgstr "9. Senior Mendicants "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 81. Vāhanasutta → bāhunasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an10.81:0.3"
msgid "81. Vāhanasutta "
msgstr "81. With Bāhuna "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.81:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā campāyaṃ viharati gaggarāya pokkharaṇiyā tīre. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Campā on the banks of the Gaggarā Lotus Pond. "

#. VAR: vāhano → bāhuno (bj, pts1) | vāhuno (s1-3)
msgctxt "an10.81:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā vāhano yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā vāhano bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Venerable Bāhuna went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.81:1.3"
msgid "“katihi nu kho, bhante, dhammehi tathāgato nissaṭo visaṃyutto vippamutto vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharatī”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, how many things has the Realized One escaped from, so that he lives unattached, liberated, his mind free of limits?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.152, sc2
msgctxt "an10.81:2.1"
msgid "“Dasahi kho, vāhana, dhammehi tathāgato nissaṭo visaṃyutto vippamutto vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharati. "
msgstr "“Bāhuna, the Realized One has escaped from ten things, so that he lives unattached, liberated, his mind free of limits. "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi dasahi? "
msgstr "What ten? "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.3"
msgid "Rūpena kho, vāhana, tathāgato nissaṭo visaṃyutto vippamutto vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharati, "
msgstr "Form … "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.4"
msgid "vedanāya kho, vāhana … pe … "
msgstr "feeling … "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.5"
msgid "saññāya kho, vāhana … "
msgstr "perception … "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.6"
msgid "saṅkhārehi kho, vāhana … "
msgstr "choices … "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.7"
msgid "viññāṇena kho, vāhana … "
msgstr "consciousness … "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.8"
msgid "jātiyā kho, vāhana … "
msgstr "rebirth … "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.9"
msgid "jarāya kho, vāhana … "
msgstr "old age … "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.10"
msgid "maraṇena kho, vāhana … "
msgstr "death … "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.11"
msgid "dukkhehi kho, vāhana … "
msgstr "suffering … "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.12"
msgid "kilesehi kho, vāhana, tathāgato nissaṭo visaṃyutto vippamutto vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharati. "
msgstr "defilements … "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.13"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, vāhana, uppalaṃ vā padumaṃ vā puṇḍarīkaṃ vā udake jātaṃ udake saṃvaḍḍhaṃ udakā paccuggamma ṭhitaṃ anupalittaṃ udakena; "
msgstr "Suppose there was a blue water lily, or a pink or white lotus. Though it sprouted and grew in the water, it would rise up above the water and stand with no water clinging to it. "

msgctxt "an10.81:2.14"
msgid "evamevaṃ kho, vāhana, imehi dasahi dhammehi tathāgato nissaṭo visaṃyutto vippamutto vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharatī”ti. "
msgstr "In the same way, the Realized One has escaped from ten things, so that he lives unattached, liberated, his mind free of limits.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.81:2.15"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

